N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 1932.5 - Reserve requirements

State Regulations

The corporation may require that the following reserves
be created by the eligible applicant, including: (a) working capital fund; (b) replacement reserve; and
(c) operating reserve. Notes
